<h3 id="_ebay_feedback">5.4. eBay feedback</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>plentymarkets gives you the possibility to automatically evaluate a purchaser positively after the purchase has been made or when you received a positive evaluation. In order for this to happen you will need to set up a procedure in the <strong>procedure manager</strong> and you will need to save some <strong>feedback texts</strong>. This procedure is the only one that can be set up with the procedure manager that does not depend on a certain point in time but is rather triggered by an event. For further information, refer to the <strong>Automatic feedback</strong> page of the manual.</p>
